---
title: Cauliflower Mac and Cheese with Blue Cheese Crumb and Sriracha Drizzle
description: Our Cauliflower Mac and Cheese is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cauliflower-mac-and-cheese-78dca008-a76b3849.jpg
